  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dd2 3 \u0d9a \u0d9a\u0dda\u0dbb\u0dc5 \u0d9c\u0d82\u0da2\u0dcf \u0dba\u0dcf\u0db4\u0db1\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "3 crore worth of Kerala ganja seized from Jaffna",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The navy said that a stock of 93 kilos of 200 grams of Kerala ganja worth nearly three crore rupees was seized today (19) at Madagall, Saukkadee beach area, Jaffna.",
        "During a special patrol carried out by the Sri Lanka Naval Ship Agbo, belonging to the Northern Naval Command, in Madagall, Soukkadi beach area, it was found that 40 parcels were packed in a box on the Soukkadi beach, and because of the naval operations, the cannabis stock may have been left behind in a sea box. said the army."
      ],
